Gustaf III King Of SWEDEN

Gustaf III King Of was born in Kungshuset, Stockholm, Stockholm, Sweden. He died on March 29th, 1792 in Stockholm Slott, Stockholm, Sweden. He was buried in Riddarholmskyrkan, Stockholm, Stockholm, Sweden.

Sofia Magdalena Queen Of SWEDEN

Sofia Magdalena Queen Of was born on July 3rd, 1746 in Christiansborg Castle, K2benhavn, K2benhavn, Denmark and her baptism took place on July 4th, 1746 in Christiansborg Slot, K2benhavn, K2benhavn, Denmark. She died at the age of 67 on August 21st, 1813 in Ulriksdal Slott, Solna, Stockholm, Sweden. She was buried in Riddarholmskyrkan, Stockholm, Stockholm, Sweden.

Gustav IV Adolf King Of SWEDEN

Gustav IV Adolf King Of was born on November 1st, 1778 in Royal Palace, Stockholm, Stockholm, Sweden and his baptism took place there on November 9th, 1778. He died at the age of 58 on February 7th, 1837 in Saint Gallen, Saint Gallen, Switzerland. He was buried in 1884 in Riddarholmkyrkan, Stockholm, Stockholm, Sweden.

Carl Gustaf Prince Of SWEDEN

Carl Gustaf Prince Of was born on August 25th, 1782 in Drottningholm Slott, Lovho, Stockholm, Sweden. He died at 6 months old on March 23rd, 1783.
